divs: Sighting DetailsI'm not the witness, but you may want to go to youtube and type in "ufo dallas", and then hit the most recent button. 3 people recorded something that almost looks CGI, but since 3 people captured it, you may want to check it out. Also type in "ufo new york" and hit the most recent button. 2 people captured this one. It too almost looks fake, but like the Dallas UFO, it may be worth checking out since it too was recorded by more than one person. Both incidents happened last night during the eclipse.
Summary: 3 record Dallas UFO, 2 record New York UFO
